data.description: A shining jewel in the most prestigious Golf community of Timberline in Calera.  This 4 bedroom 3.5 bath is just what you have been looking for.  Brazilian Cherry and Maple HW. 3 Car garage main and 1 in BSMT. Vaulted and Trey ceilings, Laundry room, Dining room and Study. Beautiful Kitchen/Keeping room with Fireplace is right out of a dream.  Gas cooktop and stainless appliances. Great room has Vaulted ceilings and built in book cases on each side of the gorgeous 2nd Fireplace.  Master suite has a sitting areas and double French doors to screened in deck.  Master bath features separate vanities and walk in closest.  Upstairs boasts 3 large bedrooms with bonus. With the basement finished with the most outstanding music room , gym and pool room you are going to be the home for all celebrations. Fenced in yard and open patio. With Plantation shutters and Arched doorways just add the perfect charm. Schedule to view it today.
